r\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19342,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/17\/hereafter-jannah-nar-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":33972,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Paradise and Hellfire pray for believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever asks Allah for Paradise three times, Paradise will say: O Allah, admit him into Paradise! Whoever seeks protection from Hellfire three times, Hellfire will say: O Allah, save him from the Hellfire!\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":843,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/06\/08\/cruel-not-enter-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":33972,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Cruelty: Harsh, mean people do not enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Harithah ibn Wahb reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNeither the haughty, nor the cruel, will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4801 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u062b\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e